#: ../../source/ServerDriver.rst:34
msgid "3 校准"
msgstr "3 Calibration"

#: ../../source/ServerDriver.rst:37
msgid "3.1 步骤"
msgstr "3.1 Steps"

#: ../../source/ServerDriver.rst:38
msgid "在驱动软件上切换到\"校准\"标签栏"
msgstr "Switch to the Calibration tab on the driver software"

#: ../../source/ServerDriver.rst:39
msgid "不要接触座椅的圆盘, 并按下驱动软件上的\"开始校准\"按键"
msgstr "Do not touch the foot pedal and press the start calibration button on the driver software"

#: ../../source/ServerDriver.rst:40
msgid "坐在座椅上，双脚自然地放在座椅圆盘上，分别在前、后、左、右四个方向上，依照自己的力量踩到觉得舒适的最大值。达到一定值以后，驱动软件界面上对应的箭头将显示为绿色。"
msgstr "Sitting on the seat, your feet are naturally placed on the foot pedal, and step on the maximum comfort level according to your own strength in the four directions of front, rear, left and right. After reaching a certain value, the corresponding arrow on the driver software interface will be displayed in green."

#: ../../source/ServerDriver.rst:41
msgid "接上一步骤，用脚将圆盘分别顺时针和逆时针旋转到自己觉得舒适的最大角度。达到一定值以后，驱动软件界面上对应的箭头将显示为绿色。"
msgstr "Continue with the previous step and use your feet to rotate the pedal clockwise and counterclockwise to the maximum angle you feel comfortable with. After reaching a certain value, the corresponding arrow on the driver software interface will be displayed in green."

#: ../../source/ServerDriver.rst:42
msgid "确保上述六个方向(前、后、左、右、顺时针旋转、逆时针旋转)对应的箭头都变为绿色，点击\"完成校准\"，此时该配置将被写入本地文件并永久保存。"
msgstr "Make sure that the arrows corresponding to the above six directions (front, back, left, right, clockwise rotation, counterclockwise rotation) are all turned green, click \"Complete calibration\", then the configuration will be permanently saved to the local file."

#: ../../source/ServerDriver.rst:45
msgid "3.2 目的"
msgstr "3.2 Purpose"

#: ../../source/ServerDriver.rst:47
msgid "校准的目的有两个:"
msgstr "Calibration has two purposes:"

#: ../../source/ServerDriver.rst:49
msgid "根据每台设备的硬件传感器数值进行调教，确保输出正确数值;"
msgstr "Adjust according to the hardware sensor value of each device to ensure that the correct value is output;"

#: ../../source/ServerDriver.rst:50
msgid "记录用户自身的使用习惯。"
msgstr "Record the user's own usage habits."

#: ../../source/ServerDriver.rst:52
msgid "一般来说只需要在第一次使用时进行一次，对操作敏感的用户也可以针对不同用户和不同的游戏分别进行校准"
msgstr "Generally speaking, it only needs to be done once when it is used for the first time. Users who are sensitive to operations can also calibrate separately for different games."

#: ../../source/ServerDriver.rst:57
msgid "4 设置"
msgstr "4 Settings"

#: ../../source/ServerDriver.rst:60
msgid "4.1 步骤"
msgstr "4.1 Steps"

#: ../../source/ServerDriver.rst:61
msgid "在驱动软件上切换到\"设置\"标签栏;"
msgstr "Switch to the \"Settings\" tab on the driver software;"

#: ../../source/ServerDriver.rst:62
msgid "选择\"模式\"( :ref:`mode-label`);"
msgstr "Select \"Mode\"( :ref:`mode-label`);"

#: ../../source/ServerDriver.rst:63
msgid "调节\"灵敏度\"( :ref:`sensitivity-label`);"
msgstr "Adjust \"Sensitivity\"( :ref:`sensitivity-label`);"

#: ../../source/ServerDriver.rst:64
msgid "调节\"速度\"( :ref:`speed-label`);"
msgstr "Adjust \"speed\"( :ref:`speed-label`);"

#: ../../source/ServerDriver.rst:65
msgid "配置\"前方\"( :ref:`forward-label`);"
msgstr "Configure \"front\"( :ref:`forward-label`);"

#: ../../source/ServerDriver.rst:66
msgid "上述步骤完成后，需要点击\"应用\"对设置进行应用和保存。"
msgstr "After the above steps are completed, you need to click \"Apply\" to apply and save the settings."

#: ../../source/ServerDriver.rst:69
msgid "4.2 目的"
msgstr "4.2 Purpose"

#: ../../source/ServerDriver.rst:70
msgid "设置的目的是根据使用场景的需要，配置硬件的使用模式、灵敏度、速度等，这些内容与校准结果保存在相同的ini文件中。"
msgstr "The purpose of the setting is to configure the usage mode, sensitivity, speed, etc. of the hardware according to the needs of the usage scenario, which are saved in the same ini file as the calibration result."

#: ../../source/ServerDriver.rst:75
msgid "4.3 模式"
msgstr "4.3 Mode"

#: ../../source/ServerDriver.rst:76
msgid "Sitwalk设置了三种操作模式。"
msgstr "Sitwalk has three modes of operation."

#: ../../source/ServerDriver.rst:78
msgid "\"正常模式\"适用于一般VR游戏的使用场景，座椅可以根据圆盘的控制自由的进行旋转。"
msgstr "\"Normal mode\"It is suitable for use in general VR games, and the seat can be freely rotated according to the control of the foot paddle."

#: ../../source/ServerDriver.rst:79
msgid "\"驾驶模式\"适用于驾驶模拟类游戏，该模式下启用了游戏方向盘的输入(DirectXInput),并且座椅只能在以\"正前方\"为中心的正负15°的范围内旋转，用以模拟车辆驾驶的情形。"
msgstr "\"Driving mode\" is suitable for driving simulation games. In this mode, the input of the game steering wheel (DirectXInput) is enabled, and the seat can only be rotated within a range of plus or minus 15° centered on the \"front\" , to simulate the driving situation of the vehicle."

#: ../../source/ServerDriver.rst:80
msgid "\"手柄模式\"适用于用户使用游戏手柄进行的VR及非VR游戏, 该模式下启用了手柄的输入(XInput),座椅的旋转由手柄的摇杆控制，可以自由旋转。"
msgstr "\"Gamepad mode\" is suitable for VR and non-VR games performed by the user using the gamepad. In this mode, the input of the handle (XInput) is enabled, and the rotation of the seat is controlled by the joystick of the handle and can be rotated freely."

#: ../../source/ServerDriver.rst:85
msgid "4.4 灵敏度"
msgstr "4.4 Sensitivity"

#: ../../source/ServerDriver.rst:86
msgid "为了防止误触，Sitwalk与绝大多数游戏控制器一样，设置了一个\"盲区\",该盲区在前后、左右、旋转轴向上均起作用。"
msgstr "In order to prevent accidental touches, Sitwalk, like most game controllers, sets up a \"blind zone\", which works on the front and rear, left and right, and the rotation axis."

#: ../../source/ServerDriver.rst:87
msgid "以0.1为例，它表示在前后、左右、旋转轴向上，当前值的绝对值小于最大值的10%时不起作用。"
msgstr "Taking 0.1 as an example, it means that it does not work when the absolute value of the current value is less than 10% of the maximum value in the front and rear, left and right, and rotation axes."

#: ../../source/ServerDriver.rst:88
msgid "可以根据自己的习惯设置合适的盲区范围，我们限制该值范围为[0~0.4]，建议的取值为0.1~0.3。"
msgstr "You can set the appropriate blind zone range according to your own habits. We limit the value range to [0~0.4], and the recommended value is 0.1~0.3."

#: ../../source/ServerDriver.rst:93
msgid "4.5 速度"
msgstr "4.5 Speed"

#: ../../source/ServerDriver.rst:94
msgid ""
"在校准过后，仍可以通过速度对输入值进行比例缩小。 "
"以\"左右\"为例，若设置值为50，意味着在左右方向上踩下到最大程度，也只能向游戏输出-0.5(左)和0.5(右)。游戏中左右的最大值为[-1~1]。"
" 该选项可以针对不同的游戏方便的调节移动和旋转的速度。"
msgstr ""
"After calibration, the input value can still be scaled down by speed. "
"Taking \"left and right\" as an example, if the value is set to 50, it means that if you step on the left and right direction to the maximum, you can only output -0.5 (left) and 0.5 (right) to the game. The maximum value of left and right in the game is [-1~1]."
" This option can easily adjust the speed of movement and rotation for different games."

#: ../../source/ServerDriver.rst:101
msgid "4.6 设置前方"
msgstr "4.6 Setting forward"

#: ../../source/ServerDriver.rst:107
msgid "按下\"顺时针旋转\"和\"逆时针旋转\"按钮，会分别让座椅按照顺时针和逆时针的方向旋转;"
msgstr "Press the \"clockwise\" and \"counter-clockwise\" buttons to rotate the seat clockwise and counterclockwise respectively;"

#: ../../source/ServerDriver.rst:108
msgid "当旋转座椅到合适的方位后(例如正对电脑显示器),按下\"设置当前朝向为前方\"按钮。"
msgstr "When the seat is rotated to a suitable orientation (for example, facing the computer monitor), press the \"set current orientation to the front\" button."

#: ../../source/ServerDriver.rst:113
msgid "5 启用座椅旋转"
msgstr "5 Enable seat rotation"

#: ../../source/ServerDriver.rst:117
msgid "出于安全考虑，在启用旋转之前，座椅是无法进行旋转的。"
msgstr "For safety reasons, the seat cannot be rotated until rotation is enabled."

